Hype meter icons turn green on movies you are following for quick reference. You wouldn t like them when they re angry. All movie trailers unlocked by default. It s like a freakin movie theater up in this app now iOS 7 Design enhancements We pretty much sat in front of the computer going: Enhance. Enhance. Enhance. Facebook sharing now includes hashtags Because we re into that whole brevity thing Fixes bug many users experienced where all movies were listed as OUT TODAY when they weren t I really have nothing funny to say about this it was an egregious error I mean the app serves one purpose to countdown to movies and it wasn t working. Thanks for your patience though!
